                     <interp inst="t17970215-15-punish77" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="publicWhipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970215-15-defend177 t17970215-15-punish77"></join>
               publicly whipped
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
